data.description: **Seller Motivated!** Welcome to your dream coastal retreat in the serene heart of Ormond Beach! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and coastal living. Nestled in a quiet and peaceful neighborhood, this property provides the ideal backdrop for a relaxed and laid-back lifestyle.    One of the standout features of this home is the airconditioned Florida room, a versatile space that can be used year-round. Whether you want to enjoy your morning coffee, read a book, or simply unwind and soak in the Florida sunshine, this room is the perfect oasis.    Step outside into your private backyard, a lush and tranquil haven where you can host barbecues, garden, or simply bask in the Florida sun. The privacy and serenity of the backyard make it an ideal space for outdoor activities and relaxation. You can hear the sound of serene waves of the Atlantic in your back yard!    One of the most incredible aspects of this property is its location. In just a short 5-minute walk, you can find yourself at the breathtaking Atlantic Ocean. Imagine taking leisurely strolls along the sandy shores, watching sunrises or sunsets, and feeling the gentle ocean breeze whenever you want.    For those who enjoy dining out and shopping, you're in luck! Hop on your bike and take a leisurely ride to Granada Blvd, where you'll discover a variety of upscale dining options and boutique shopping experiences. This lively area adds an extra layer of convenience and entertainment to your coastal lifestyle.    In summary, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Ormond Beach offers not only a comfortable and well-appointed living space but also an unbeatable location that allows you to fully embrace the coastal lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this tranquil haven your own and experience the best of beachside living. Your dream home awaits!
